ZH: 我用粉笔在黑板上写字。
EN: I write on the blackboard with chalk.

ZH: 老师在课堂上用粉笔讲解。
EN: The teacher uses chalk to explain in the classroom.

ZH: 粉笔的颜色是白色的。
EN: Chalk is white in color.

ZH: 这个学校使用粉笔教学。
EN: This school uses chalk for teaching.

ZH: 请给我一块粉笔。
EN: Please give me a piece of chalk.

ZH: 粉笔盒里还有几块粉笔。
EN: There are a few more pieces of chalk in the chalk box.

ZH: 学生们喜欢在课堂上玩粉笔。
EN: Students like to play with chalk in the classroom.

ZH: 老师用粉笔画了一幅漂亮的图画。
EN: The teacher drew a beautiful picture with chalk.

ZH: 他不小心把粉笔弄断了。
EN: He accidentally broke the chalk.

ZH: 哥哥总是在课堂上扔粉笔。
EN: My older brother always throws chalk in the classroom.

ZH: 粉笔在手上会留下白色的印记。
EN: Chalk leaves a white mark on your hands.

ZH: 这个教室的黑板没有粉笔。
EN: There is no chalk on the blackboard in this classroom.

ZH: 老师微笑着接过我的粉笔。
EN: The teacher smiled as she took my chalk.

ZH: 我用湿海绵把黑板上的粉笔擦掉。
EN: I use a wet sponge to erase the chalk on the blackboard.

ZH: 这片地上有一块粉笔。
EN: There is a piece of chalk on the floor.

ZH: 弟弟喜欢咬粉笔。
EN: My younger brother likes to bite chalk.

ZH: 教室里有很多不同颜色的粉笔。
EN: There are many different colors of chalk in the classroom.

ZH: 妹妹画了一只粉笔盒上的小猫。
EN: My sister drew a little cat on the chalk box.

ZH: 学生们用粉笔写下了课堂笔记。
EN: The students wrote down their class notes with chalk.

ZH: 老师拿起粉笔指着黑板上的问题。
EN: The teacher picked up the chalk and pointed to the question on the blackboard.
